Author: Ivan Petek
Title: [ANN][ICO] IIOTTEL - Industrial Internet of Things on Blockchain
Body: How to USE Token in Industrial Internet of Things on Blockchain  International company providing high-margin services, usually do not pay attention to the fee and speed of payments. If the payment is late they can easily apply to court to recover the debt. Though if the payment is only $1–2, and not often, what do we do? Then the fee become significant, and the speed and commitment of payment is critical.  Although we have alternative way. The company IIoT Telecom issues its own crypto currency I2, which will be accepted as the only one payment for Services provided by IIoT Platform. This is the same cryptocurrency, from which company plans to get financing from the ICO (initial coin offering)..   https://medium.com/@iiottel/how-to-use-token-in-industrial-internet-of-things-on-blockchain-9d7cc5bb7419

Body: OP, I have been following this project from very nearby (as you probably know). I think this might be huge and (r)evolve IoT/IIoT, making it cheaper, simpler to use and using A LOT less energy, thus also making it a lot more environment-friendly.  However, if I may say so, although I know the Industries will be a very important player in this project, I think it would be very useful to explain on this forum not only in easily understandable language, but also in only a few lines, what exactly the use, the idea and the ambition of the project is.  This forum is flooded with newbies and juniors looking for interesting opportunities to invest and/or speculate, who are missing out on this impressive project, because their attention span is not longer than 20 seconds.  And I think a lot of the more serious investors and readers on this forum could be interested in the project too, and a short introduction could awaken their curiosity. Because if this one breaks through, you will have a hell of a giant company and there could be many crying for having missed out on this project.  Well, that's just my modest opinion!  Again, all the best for IIoT.tel! I am supporting

Title: [ANN][ICO] IIOTTEL - Industrial Internet of Things on Blockchain
Body: Two options of cooperation: STRAIGHT FRANCHISE - The Franchisee purchases the franchise. Size of initial contribution has not yet been determined and will be discussed. The Franchisee receives the rights to use our brand, the IIoT Platform as an administrator, and LoRaWAN devices and sensors at the dealer price (with significant discount). He is assigned a group of engineers providing technical aspects. The Franchisee receives the exclusive right of a city/district REVERSE FRANCHISE - The Franchisee purchases the franchise. Size of initial contribution has not yet been determined and will be discussed. The Franchisee receives the rights to use our brand, the IIoT Platform as an administrator, and LoRaWAN devices and sensors at the dealer price (with significant discount). He is assigned a group of engineers providing technical aspects. The Franchisee receives the exclusive right of a city/district. For more detail see page 54 WP.

Any dealer with solutions in the field of IoT will be able to use the ready infrastructure in any city in the world. In fact, it is a universal tool for Blockchain and the tokenization of any Industrial Internet of Things solution, even if originally it was not planned for use in Blockchain. The IIoT Platform will have a special Marketplace component for connecting Partners. We have agreements with several interested enterprises, but there is probably no need to sign them in a traditional way. In the IIoT Platform, all agreements will be broken in the form of smart contracts.

Author: iiottel
Title: [ANN][ICO] IIOTTEL - Industrial Internet of Things on Blockchain
Body: WEBSITE IIOT.TEL  >>>  WHITEPAPER | BISINESS PLAN | PROMO <<<  >>>  BOUNTY CAMPAIGN <<<  >>>  Telegram Chat for Support <<<     Innovation squared - Industrial Internet of Things on the Blockchain (The new formula of innovation: I2=IIoT+Blockchain)  Our mission Create the international innovative Company, which technological and information solutions will allow to improve existing business processes of companies and people's daily lives through implementation products of the Industrial Internet of things.  IIoT Telecom The core business of the company includes two components – one is the decentralized IIoT Platform and the other is wireless network LoRaWan, that based on equipment of its own design.    IIoT Platform – decentralized specialized software on the Blockchain, allows to gather information from numerous "smart" IIoT devices, saves these data in  the Blockchain, processes the data according to the special algorithms. The information may be send to separate external Customer’s business support system (OSS/BSS), and provide visualization and analysis of the obtained data in the personal account of the Customer and the Client.  The Blockchain technology makes IIoT Platform to be high availability and independent.    Our goals The goal of our Company is getting the profits through the Services of Industrial Internet of things in the global market. Capture no less than 0,0022% of the global market share of the Internet of things .  How does it work     Pre-ICO Starts: February 19, 2018 Token Price: $0.1 per token Ends: March 18, 2018  You can get 50% discount when buy I2 tokens  ICO Bonuses on the first 30 days  the first ten-day period - bonus 30%    the second ten-day period  - bonus 20%    the third ten-day period  - bonus 10%    ICO Bonuses on the next 31 days  10% OFF for purchase from $900 to $3,000.  20% OFF for purchase from $3,001 to $9,999.  And 30% OFF when buying in the amount of $10,000.   ICO Starts: March 19, 2018 Token Price: $0.1 per token. Ends: May 19, 2018    Roadmap    Team    >>>  WHITEPAPER | BISINESS PLAN | PROMO <<<  >>>  JOIN US <<<

Author: Ivan Petek
Title: [ANN][ICO] IIOTTEL - Industrial Internet of Things on Blockchain
Body: And the second  IOTA is first in IoT. IIoT Telecom will be first in IIoT on Blockchain. Do you know what’s difference?  The Internet of things (IoT) and Industrial Internet of things (IIoT) is similar in principle of operation and the name of the technology, but are designed for different tasks. These technologies are developing in parallel, and hardly ever have any intersection in future.  These are completely different concepts, the similarity between which is only in abbreviations and high-level concepts. But if you concentrate on the details, these concepts go hand in hand sometimes, borrowing some plans one from another.  IOTA is First in IoT. IIoT Telecom is planning to be First in IIoT. Where IoT is applied today? https://medium.com/@iiottel/iota-is-first-in-iot-80e4f32b59e
